text: We’re so excited to have Cheyenne Lindsey, a sign language interpreter, at the health dept today from JCIL! An interpreter is available until 11 a.m. and again from 1-3 p.m. today to help people coming to get a #COVID19 #vaccine who are deaf or hard of hearing. #ThisIsOurShot https://t.co/GiZgszBDSz
